OL,7,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,8,F(PSNI) Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,9,Fhas confirmed he will provide a public
OL,10,Freport on the extent of police
OL,11,Fsurveillance of lawyers and
OL,12,Fjournalists, the Policing Board has
OL,13,Fsaid.
