OL,3,CBoutcher set to deliver report on
OL,4,Cclaims police spied on journalists and
OL,5,Clawyers
OL,7,FThe leadership of the board, the
OL,8,Foversight body for the PSNI, said it
OL,9,Fhad told Mr Boutcher that "damage is
OL,10,Fbeing done" to public confidence in
OL,11,Fpolicing by claims made during a
OL,12,Ftribunal hearing that surveillance was
OL,13,Fcarried out on the phone data of
OL,14,Fjournalists.
OL,16,FBoard chairman Mukesh Sharma and vice
OL,17,Fchairman Brendan Mullan met Mr
OL,18,FBoutcher on Wednesday.
