OL,5,Clawyers
OL,7,FA hearing of the Investigatory Powers
OL,8,FTribunal (IPT) in London last week
OL,9,Fheard claims that police in Northern
OL,10,FIreland undertook six-monthly trawls
OL,11,Fof the phone data of "troublemaker"
OL,12,Fjournalists to see if they were in
OL,13,Fcontact with officer sources.
OL,15,FIt came during a hearing of a case
OL,16,Fexamining allegations that
OL,17,Finvestigative reporters Barry
OL,18,FMcCaffrey and Trevor Birney were
OL,19,Fsubject to unlawful covert
OL,20,Fintelligence by the police.
