OL,7,F"Our human rights adviser will also
OL,8,Fhave full access to all the material
OL,9,Fthat informs the report in order to
OL,10,Fprovide assurance on legal compliance.
OL,12,F"The Chief Constable shares our
OL,13,Fconcerns and has advised that he
OL,14,Fintends to develop an additional
OL,15,Freview mechanism to examine and
OL,16,Faddress the issues raised."
