OL,7,FThe statement added: "Today's meeting
OL,8,Fwas constructive, and we welcome the
OL,9,Fcontinued commitment of the Chief
OL,10,FConstable to openness and
OL,11,Ftransparency."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, two human rights
OL,14,Forganisations, Amnesty International
OL,15,Fand the Committee on the
OL,16,FAdministration of Justice (CAJ), have
OL,17,Fwritten to the board, making a fresh
OL,18,Fcall for an inquiry into the claims.
