OL,7,FThe letter from the two organisations
OL,8,Fsaid the IPT case "has now revealed
OL,9,Fthat covert surveillance has been
OL,10,Fdeployed against journalists on
OL,11,Fmultiple occasions over the period of
OL,12,Fat least a decade".
OL,14,FIt continues: "It now appears that
OL,15,Fthere was routine surveillance of the
OL,16,Fphone data of journalists, and
OL,17,Fpossible surveillance of the spouse of
OL,18,Fone journalist as well as their lawyer.
