OL,7,F"Further, we understand that the
OL,8,Flimited disclosure of information to
OL,9,Fdate by the Chief Constable to the
OL,10,FPolicing Board points to multiple
OL,11,Finstances of covert surveillance by
OL,12,Fthe PSNI of journalists and lawyers.
OL,14,F"Public disquiet at the intrusive,
OL,15,Fcovert and possibly unlawful use of
OL,16,Fsurveillance powers by the PSNI is
OL,17,Fconsiderable.
