OL,7,F"The partial and drip-feed disclosure
OL,8,Fof relevant information by the PSNI,
OL,9,Fboth to the IPT and to the Policing
OL,10,FBoard is further undermining public
OL,11,Fconfidence in policing here."
OL,13,FThe two organisations urged the board
OL,14,Fto establish an inquiry under the
OL,15,FPolice (Northern Ireland) Act 2000.
